videos.headline: Vaughn barrels into the end zone
videos.description: Vanderbilt running back Ke'Shawn Vaughn bulldozes into the end zone for the 5-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Vandy recovers the fumble for the long TD
videos.description: Kentucky running back Asim Rose fumbles the football and Vanderbilt's Allan George returns it 67 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Rodriguez scores 2nd TD of game for Kentucky
videos.description: Christopher Rodriguez Jr.'s big day continues as he scores his second touchdown to put Kentucky up 38-14 over Vanderbilt.
